{"tid":1068450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那新娘下體任人摸 婚鬧變成多P大戰","createTime":"2019-03-19T08:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T10:24:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fd655b2ed61a31fd747b7fad03f8f5f3fff34fcd","tid":1068450,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"中國變態婚鬧無極限，讓人看了直搖頭，即便政府大肆宣導停止這種惡質婚鬧，但還是不時出現。就在前日，甘肅一場婚禮上，再度出現變態婚鬧。<br />\n<br />\n據中國微博網友指出，這場在甘肅的婚禮上，公公被逼著穿上奇裝異服，揹著新娘進家門，但在這過程中，旁邊的賓客卻趁機偷吃新娘的豆腐，不時亂摸新娘的下體與屁股，相當猥褻。另一段婚鬧影片，則是新郎新娘與眾賓客玩耍助興，但現場卻看到一堆人不分男女，衝上一名伴娘的身體，更看到有男生直接扒下伴娘的絲襪和內褲。而在一旁的其他女賓，也被男賓抱著玩，整段婚鬧頓時間變成「多P大戰」。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友們紛紛直呼：「噁心。」、「為什麼不報警？有病吧。」、「下流。」、「永遠無法文明。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASagezm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASagezm.jpg&h=eefd6929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvPHUzn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvPHUzn.jpg&h=26eb0cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UrnUzn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UrnUzn.jpg&h=270d2b23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d923e2e47e6e24c9de71d4fb1c2e22da87f30279","tid":1068450,"uid":133529,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"樓主，有圖係唔夠架，你知道嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8831d354d049f0076e945aa9cec7aa88addfbce","tid":1068450,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914c2fc067283f84b6c3bc3862ff5b21a9a4726f","tid":1068450,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":67,"score":-66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code>